&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;This would create a new zone of fun and bring back what made the original PoM so fun. This would also add armor quests for groups in their mid 50's-early 60's on top of giving high levels unique clickies and other fun toys that they can enjoy.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
