&lt;P&gt;There is no longer enough space to keep everything, especially with the new tradeskill quests. The guild bank has 200 slots, perhaps the individual character's bank could be similar. If we had 200 slots, which could also hold containers with items in - but the container couldn't be opened until taken out of the bank, then we would no longer&amp;nbsp;have to worry about space. Also, having this much space would allow us to organise our bank better, by for example only putting into a quest container items for that quest.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;7.&amp;nbsp; Plane of Mischief Questing:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;1. Add Plane of Mischief cards to other named loot tables with a realistic drop rate. To be specific, making the drop rates about 75% of the time to drop "common" cards with a 50/50 chance to drop a "rare" card. One A White Stallion that spawns once every three days is a bit tedious for us questers since farmers will just farm this mob for the profit and sell the cards. Which detracts from the total fun of the original zone.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;2. Put back in the Knight cards please.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
