&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;4 common-&amp;gt;1 uncommon&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;4 uncommon=rare&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;Or have new quests that grant cards as rewards.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;4. Reinstate all original rewards with all the old cards.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;FONT color=#cccccc&gt;www.planeofmischief.com/items.htm&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;FONT color=#cccccc&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;6.&amp;nbsp; Add in a new armor set that is on par for the level of the zone with unique foci and crazy clickies. Perhaps even adding new color cards and new combinations to signify the rewards system&amp;nbsp;increase &amp;nbsp;that has occured since these quests were first implement.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;7. Make a use for Jester cards.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;This would create a new zone of fun and bring back what made the original PoM so fun. This would also add armor quests for groups in their mid 50's-early 60's on top of giving high levels unique clickies and other fun toys that they can enjoy.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;8.&amp;nbsp; Fix broken tasks&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;The following tasks are believed broken. Please see the seperate Broken Tasks forum for details. (Some might be fixed now, but it doesn't say so!)&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;UL&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Lost in Petrification &lt;/STRONG&gt;- Kill 10 sathirian protectors in DL.&amp;nbsp; No such mob exists. &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Whirling Dervish&lt;/STRONG&gt;, a short task.&amp;nbsp;- Explore the iksar tower on the north-east island of Timorous Deep. Task does not update. &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Wooly Adventures &lt;/STRONG&gt;- There is no blue compass line directing you to Droganoth Hrothgar in Everfrost Peaks. &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Scary Caves&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;from Dreadlands - It says to explore the courtyard on the left just inside the castle. But it doesn't trigger unless you go to the courtyard on the right just inside the castle.&amp;nbsp; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Keeping Order &lt;/STRONG&gt;- Exploring the entrance of the cave in Firiona Vie that leads to the dreadlands doesn't update the task. &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Keeping The Goblins Out &lt;/STRONG&gt;from Lavastorm - The task does not update when you loot&amp;nbsp;Cinder Goblin Toes. &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Drolvargs and Drachnids &lt;/STRONG&gt;- Exploring the ruins in the center of the forest of the firiona vie zone doesn't update the task.&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;9.&amp;nbsp; Broken Quests&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Please see the forum about &lt;A href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Quests&amp;amp;message.id=345" target=_blank&gt;&lt;FONT color=#fac400&gt;broken or unfinished quests&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/A&gt;, and respond.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;10.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Factions Button&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Add a button to the inventory screen to list factions, ideally indicating how close you are to the next level.&amp;nbsp;As there are so many factions, perhaps only list those that are not indiff, or perhaps have a factions window with a tab for each of the nine faction stages, from 'Ready to Attack' to 'Ally'.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
