&lt;P&gt;Please see the forum about &lt;FONT color=#fac400&gt;&lt;A href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Quests&amp;amp;message.id=43" target=_blank&gt;broken or unfinished tasks&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;, and respond.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
