&lt;UL&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Lost in Petrification &lt;/STRONG&gt;- Kill 10 sathirian protectors in DL.&amp;nbsp; No such mob exists.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Whirling Dervish&lt;/STRONG&gt;, a short task.&amp;nbsp;- Explore the iksar tower on the north-east island of Timorous Deep. Task does not update.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Wooly Adventures &lt;/STRONG&gt;- There is no blue compass line directing you to Droganoth Hrothgar in Everfrost Peaks.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Scary Caves&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;from Dreadlands - It says to explore the courtyard on the left just inside the castle. But it doesn't trigger unless you go to the courtyard on the right just inside the castle.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Keeping Order &lt;/STRONG&gt;- Exploring the entrance of the cave in Firiona Vie that leads to the dreadlands doesn't update the task.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Keeping The Goblins Out &lt;/STRONG&gt;from Lavastorm - The task does not update when you loot&amp;nbsp;Cinder Goblin Toes.&lt;/LI&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Drolvargs and Drachnids &lt;/STRONG&gt;- Exploring the ruins in the center of the forest of the firiona vie zone doesn't update the task.&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;9.&amp;nbsp; Broken Quests&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Please see the forum about &lt;A href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Quests&amp;amp;message.id=345" target=_blank&gt;broken or unfinished quests&lt;/A&gt;, and respond.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;10.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Factions Button&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;BLOCKQUOTE dir=ltr&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;Add a button to the inventory screen to list factions, ideally indicating how close you are to the next level.&amp;nbsp;As there are so many factions, perhaps only list those that are not indiff, or perhaps have a factions window with a tab for each of the nine faction stages, from 'Ready to Attack' to 'Ally'.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
